text: Gnamptogenys coxalis is a species of ant of the subfamily Ectatomminae, which can be found from Borneo, Sri Lanka, India, and Nicobar Islands. ==References== ==External links== * * at antwiki.org *Animaldiversity.org *Itis.org Category:Ectatomminae Category:Hymenoptera of Asia Category:Insects described in 1860
